{"tid":157348,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"沒戴套就上！人妻裝避孕器「1次就中」　小王怒：兩光醫生","createTime":"2017-03-15T12:31:20.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-15T12:44:03.000Z","uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5099a2eb71849ef27c97030e4ea62fcb18306b9b","tid":157348,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T12:31:20.000Z","msg":"<strong>沒戴套就上！人妻裝避孕器「1次就中」　小王怒：兩光醫生</strong><br />\n2017-03-14 20:54:00<br />\n<br />\n新北市一名已婚林姓女子前年和一名康姓男子偷情，不料她裝了避孕器仍懷孕。女方發現自己有喜，用LINE將此事告知康男，還表示「推算我們第一次就中了」，而男方還大罵醫師是「兩光」，「避孕器是假的嗎？」對話事後遭人夫發現提告；新北地院判2人各3月徒刑，得易科罰金，另須賠償20萬元。<br />\n<br />\n判決指出，34歲的林女和31歲康男於2015年2月底出軌偷情，不料女方裝有避孕器仍意外懷孕，於同年3月5日前往婦產科看診；由於妻子返家後眼神、舉止怪異，讓人夫察覺有異，碰巧林女的手機在其曬衣服時響起，林夫代為查看意外發現老婆和康男的LINE對話，這才發現自己被戴綠帽。<br />\n<br />\n崩潰的人夫事後對2人提出告訴，和妻子也於2016月5月協議離婚。全案經新北地院審理，勘驗林女和康男的LINE對話後，發現女方告知自己懷孕後，並指「推算我們第一次就中了！」而小王則回答「避孕器是假的嗎？」甚至大罵「兩光醫生裝的避孕器」；而婦產科醫生也證稱，林女曾明確指小孩並不是先生的。<br />\n<br />\n法官審酌，認為全案事證明確，被告2 人犯行堪以認定，因此判處林女和康男有期徒刑3月，得易科罰金9萬元；另人夫向2人求償200萬元，認為姦情已對原告婚姻生活造成損害，因此判決須賠償20萬元；全案仍可上訴。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.bestchinanews.com/url.php?p=http://p2.qhimg.com/t017f93e9d5ed9dfd3b.gif?size=350x164\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.bestchinanews.com%2Furl.php%3Fp%3Dhttp%3A%2F%2Fp2.qhimg.com%2Ft017f93e9d5ed9dfd3b.gif%3Fsize%3D350x164&h=c4c345a9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"08beb0162e4ad4f97bf072c627f7c28833022097","tid":157348,"uid":60136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T12:32:16.000Z","msg":"新BUGS +1"},{"pid":"53f6133e7aaf6d1245ab3f079308ac753fda7e6a","tid":157348,"uid":581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T12:32:26.000Z","msg":"曼聯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1fdecb11a0e778afb399aca4b5cdd884f708a4d","tid":157348,"uid":38189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T12:35:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>曼聯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfb0e025f1f02fcbd5dcafcfdec6a9d657b672ed","tid":157348,"uid":67225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T12:42:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>曼聯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91f698f31f1b31836adb2036fc6b3a93b9bcca08","tid":157348,"uid":12543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T12:43:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f060953cb57569e823aa05e03e48803c5bc6b8a5","tid":157348,"uid":74497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T12:44:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 新北"}]}